                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210214-132-off800 t18210214-132-crimeloc803"></join>. I keep a butcher's shop. On the 30th of February, I was in the back shop - a boy said the beef was stolen; I ran out and saw the prisoner put the beef into the girl's apron and run away - we lost him; I secured the girl in about five minutes - she would not say what she had done with it. I am sure he is the boy.</p>
